while you're at it."

40:39.270 --> 40:42.387
You think I wanted to wear your
hand-me-down shirts that didn't fit?

40:42.565 --> 40:45.523
Wasn't bad enough,
my daddy died in Vietnam.

40:45.693 --> 40:47.854
My mama left me
for a Yankee race car driver.

40:48.029 --> 40:51.237
-You took shit away from me my whole life.
-We didn't have any money.

40:51.407 --> 40:55.025
You all had it all and never gave us nothing,
no matter how bad we needed it.

40:55.203 --> 40:59.287
Only reason I went into the Corps was
college, and now I'm too fucked up to go.

40:59.457 --> 41:00.537
You fucking had it all.

41:00.708 --> 41:03.871
It was Grandmama's money, you asshole,
not mine. Now it's gone.

41:04.045 --> 41:05.785
Good. That's what you fucking deserve.

41:05.964 --> 41:09.331
Yeah, but I'm a sheriff,
and you're only a fry cook, so I fucking win.

41:09.509 --> 41:10.749
Ooh....

41:10.927 --> 41:13.714
-Son of a bitch.
-Motherfucker.

41:14.597 --> 41:16.098
[GRUNTING]

41:18.309 --> 41:21.267
ANDY:
Fuck you, Terry. Easy.

41:21.896 --> 41:22.885
Shit.

41:24.190 --> 41:27.853
You shouldn't have been able
to breach my boundary.

41:28.569 --> 41:32.357
Did you acquire some new abilities
in your travels?

41:32.865 --> 41:34.571
I think I did.

41:34.909 --> 41:37.992
And you have a demon to serve you.

41:38.413 --> 41:40.244
Yeah, I don't know.

41:40.415 --> 41:43.452
l was hoping to get with Marnie
so we could figure it out together.

41:43.626 --> 41:46.584
I usually come to her
with all my questions.

41:47.755 --> 41:52.124
We spent an entire year talking about magic
and everything else.

41:52.301 --> 41:55.008
You were her most faithful ally.

41:55.638 --> 41:56.923
I still am.

41:58.850 --> 42:00.932
If our circle were stronger...

42:01.102 --> 42:07.439
...we would be able to exterminate
those vampires so much more easily.

42:08.776 --> 42:14.271
Your friend, the Moor,
is he gonna join us again?

42:14.449 --> 42:16.110
He has a gift.

42:16.284 --> 42:17.740
The Moor?

42:19.287 --> 42:21.198
Lafayette?

42:21.539 --> 42:24.747
Oh, Antonia, no.

42:24.917 --> 42:27.624
I tried. He's just really scared.

42:27.795 --> 42:30.753
But if you let us out of here
for a little while...

42:31.299 --> 42:35.008
-...I can probably bring him around.
-lmpossible.

42:36.137 --> 42:40.130
That protection spell is
our strongest defense.

42:41.267 --> 42:43.132
For now.

42:43.895 --> 42:45.806
I understand.

42:47.648 --> 42:49.184
I wonder....

42:51.194 --> 42:53.435
I don't want to be rude.

42:53.613 --> 42:55.399
Ask.

42:56.365 --> 42:58.356
You have nothing to fear from me.

42:58.534 --> 43:00.320
Can I speak with Marnie, please?

43:00.495 --> 43:06.582
-I speak on behalf of both of us.
-I know.

43:08.002 --> 43:09.742
But she's my friend...

43:10.505 --> 43:12.041
...and my teacher.

43:12.799 --> 43:16.917
I miss her, and it would be nice to
say hello in person.

43:17.095 --> 43:18.835
Just for a minute.

43:20.181 --> 43:23.093
You are a very kind man.

43:25.853 --> 43:28.310
So rare.

43:28.773 --> 43:33.187
I'm not surprised
that Marnie cares for you.

43:44.789 --> 43:46.950
-Jesus.
-Marnie?

43:47.125 --> 43:49.036
-I thought you'd abandoned me.
-Never.

43:49.210 --> 43:50.620
-Are you okay?
-Yeah.

43:50.795 --> 43:53.912
-I am magnificent.
-Are you sure?

43:54.090 --> 43:58.208
Well, can't you tell?
You ever seen me looking so happy?

43:58.386 --> 44:02.925
All due respect, you're, like, possessed.

44:03.099 --> 44:06.387
What, you think this is against my will?

44:08.729 --> 44:10.890
Oh, I'm sorry. ljust assumed.

44:11.065 --> 44:12.805
Oh, of course.

44:12.984 --> 44:15.396
How could you possibly comprehend?

44:15.570 --> 44:17.401
No,no,no.

44:17.572 --> 44:20.735
Here. Feel my vibrations
the way I taught you.

44:25.413 --> 44:26.619
Do you see?

44:27.415 --> 44:29.030
Do you see?

44:29.208 --> 44:32.666
Don't you feel our strengths?

44:33.504 --> 44:35.244
Her desires are my desires...

44:35.423 --> 44:40.292
...her ambitions my ambitions,
her enemy is mine.

44:40.469 --> 44:43.597
I am in control.

44:45.349 --> 44:51.845
This is not possession, this is union.

44:55.526 --> 44:57.938
-That's great.
-Yeah.

44:58.112 --> 44:59.272
Come on. Let me show you.

44:59.447 --> 45:01.688
We've got our own vampires
in the ladies room.

45:05.286 --> 45:06.617
1135 US:
Sookie, the game has changed.

45:06.787 --> 45:07.162
Shit.

45:07.788 --> 45:07.947
Marnie is behind this now.

45:07.955 --> 45:08.614
Marnie is behind this now.

45:08.623 --> 45:09.078
What?

45:09.248 --> 45:12.456
-Did that bitch do something to him?
-Marnie's flipped sides.

45:12.627 --> 45:14.788
-She's running this show.
-Fuck.

45:14.962 --> 45:17.499
[TARA & HOLLY SPEAKING IN LATIN]

45:29.393 --> 45:32.806
It's marvelous.
They'll do anything I want.

45:32.980 --> 45:37.189
They'll slaughter their friends,
kill each other...

45:37.360 --> 45:40.852
...eat chocolate, go to the beach.

45:41.030 --> 45:43.112
[BOTH SPEAKING IN LATIN]

45:43.908 --> 45:46.775
[BOTH GASP]

45:55.753 --> 45:57.209
Treachery.

45:57.380 --> 45:58.495
1135 US:
Sookie, get out of here!

45:58.673 --> 46:01.210
-Something's up. Jesus says run.
-Then we should run?

46:01.384 --> 46:02.999
-We can't leave them.
-Hell, no.

46:03.594 --> 46:05.095
Tara. Hurry!

46:05.263 --> 46:06.503
TARA: Run!
LAFAYETTE: Where's Jesus?

46:08.349 --> 46:09.589
TARA:
SooMe.

46:09.767 --> 46:11.553
[SPEAKING IN LATIN]

46:11.727 --> 46:13.263
JASON:
Sookie! NO. God.

46:26.200 --> 46:28.942
-Say you give up and you won't do V.
ANDY: I give up.

46:29.120 --> 46:33.409
I'll never do another drop again.
Please, I'm so scared.

46:38.713 --> 46:40.874
I'm seeing things.

46:42.717 --> 46:45.959
-You look like a monster.
-|t's me.

46:47.138 --> 46:49.880
Don't worry. It's only me.

46:50.558 --> 46:55.177
At least your visions ain't real.
Stuff | see, it all happened.

46:56.314 --> 46:58.930
You've been through so much.

47:03.362 --> 47:06.900
-I ain't got no excuse.
-I ain'tjudging you.

47:07.408 --> 47:10.992
Plenty of men come back from war
and don't live in a tree house.

47:14.081 --> 47:15.696
[PANTING]

47:15.875 --> 47:18.992
I'm so ashamed of myself I can't stand it.

47:19.920 --> 47:22.582
I don't wanna be who I am.

47:25.176 --> 47:27.508
Bringing V into a house with children...

47:27.678 --> 47:31.762
...how could I do that
without even thinking about it?

47:33.100 --> 47:35.091
What if it's ate my soul?

47:38.064 --> 47:41.147
This is what rock bottom feels like, son.

47:41.692 --> 47:45.025
There's nothing wrong
with you deep inside.

47:45.529 --> 47:47.986
You're crying, Andy.

47:48.157 --> 47:52.651
-Men without souls do not cry.
-Are you sure?

47:53.245 --> 47:55.497
Hell, yeah, I'm sure.

47:55.664 --> 47:58.656
Here. Who knows you better than me?

47:58.834 --> 48:00.370
Nobody.

48:00.544 --> 48:02.535
Not a person on this earth.

48:02.713 --> 48:04.795
-You know I'll help you any way I can.
-Yeah.

48:07.343 --> 48:10.335
-I love you, cousin.
-I love you too.

48:17.311 --> 48:19.222
l'll pull the truck around.

48:28.280 --> 48:30.487
Fort Bellefleur.

48:31.534 --> 48:33.866
I ought to spend more time here.

48:34.578 --> 48:36.864
I can see why you come back
to the tree house.

48:38.165 --> 48:40.952
Always was a good place to think.

48:42.294 --> 48:46.253
When Daddy died, when Mama left...

48:48.676 --> 48:50.712
...this is where I went.

48:53.097 --> 48:54.177
[CAR HORN HONKS]

48:54.682 --> 48:55.671
Heading for home.

48:57.935 --> 49:00.096
I'm not gonna relapse.

49:00.271 --> 49:03.013
-Gonna be a real uncle to your kids.
-I know you are.

49:03.190 --> 49:06.057
And you're gonna take your first steps
as a free man tonight...

49:06.235 --> 49:09.523
-...when you walk all the way home.
-What?

49:09.697 --> 49:12.734
Lock up the guns, sheriff.
See you at the dinner table.

49:12.908 --> 49:15.365
Terry. Terry!

49:16.036 --> 49:18.072
Goddamn it.
